source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_00<tab>Yadovv Gah is eager to seize upon his foe's miscalculation.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_00<tab>Yadovv Gah a une mission à vous confier.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_01<tab>Though he often counsels measured action, Yadovv Gah appears hungry for blood this day. It seems that certain of Zagozz Teh's elite troops have left his side, with orders to participate in upcoming raids. Take advantage of their vulnerability, and strike down the Zahar'ak lancers and archers.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_01<tab>Yadovv Gah vous a parlé d'une opportunité d'attaquer des unités de la garde spéciale du chef des Crocs de Feu. Venez à bout de trois <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072D0302 /var> et trois <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072E0302 /var> dans l'enceinte de Zahar'ak.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_02<tab>You have slain the lancers and archers of Zahar'ak, leaving their corpses as a stark warning to Zagozz Teh and his arrogance. Return to the Ring of Ash and report to Yadovv Gah.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez vaincu les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072D0302 /var> et les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072E0302 /var>. Retournez faire votre rapport au camp.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_03<tab>You return to Yadovv Gah with news of your unrestrained slaughter. Though cheered by the thought of such fangs pulled from his enemy's maw, the Brotherhood warrior warns that your attacks may provoke retaliation. Stand ready to offer your assistance should the need arise.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_SEQ_03<tab>Yadovv Gah s'est montré satisfait de votre succès, et vous exhorte à poursuivre votre en<var 16 /var>traî<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment en vue de futures missions.
TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_TODO_02<tab>Faire un rapport à Yadovv Gah

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_000<tab>Honored ally, the greed of our foes has led them into grave error.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_000<tab>Salutations, puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> guerri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>. T'entretenir des activités des Crocs de Feu, j'aimerais.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_001<tab>In his frantic quest to gather victims for tempering, Zagozz Teh has allowed certain of his personal bodyguards to join the Flamefang raiding efforts.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_001<tab>Plus assidus encore que d'ordinaire, ils semblent. Aux enlèvements, une partie de la garde rapprochée de leur chef Zagozz The prend désormais part.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_002<tab>Never again will his elite soldiers be so vulnerable! I urge you to strike now, and remove these pieces from the board.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_002<tab>Une occasion inespérée, cela pourrait être. Opportun pour une offensive décisive, le moment est.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_003<tab>You will find the high-ranked lancers and archers prowling the canyons of Zahar'ak, awaiting the call to action. Spare these fools neither words nor mercy.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_003<tab>Des cibles clefs à éliminer, j'ai déjà déterminé. Par des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072D0302 /var> et des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072E0302 /var>, nous allons commencer.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_004<tab>This day is a day for blood! May the fortune of battle be yours.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_004<tab>Vaincre trois unités de chaque groupe, tu vas. Réduire leur force de frappe, cela devrait.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_010<tab>Hunt down the Flamefang elites, and leave them bleeding in the dust. Zagozz Teh will pay for his mad ambition.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_010<tab>Trois <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072D0302 /var> et trois <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2072E0302 /var>, tu vas éliminer. Réduire leur force de frappe, cela devrait.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_020<tab>You have dealt a telling blow, honored ally. The enemy has been deprived of some of his sharpest fangs.
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_020<tab>Ta mission, tu as remarquablement accompli. Plusieurs membres d'élite, nos ennemis ont perdu. Découragés, ces maudits Crocs de Feu seront cer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment.

source: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_021<tab>But the wounded cur is most like to bite. Be on guard, and prepared to move at a moment's notice!
target: TEXT_BANAMA301_01242_YADOVVGAH_000_021<tab>Mais relâcher notre vigilance, nous ne devons pas. Poursuivre toujours nos efforts pour atteindre la force suprême et vaincre nos ennemis, nous devons. En faire de même, tu dois aussi.
